月癸酉<graphic n="KR0816" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0816.png" mimeType="image/png"/>朙年四月庚子葬<graphic n="KR0715" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0715.png" mimeType="image/png"/>是門生汝南干<hi>闕</hi>沛<lb/>
<pb n="KR2n0017_SBCK_009-5b"/>
