之<graphic n="KR0263" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0263.png" mimeType="image/png"/>報痛昊天之靡嘉頓企有紀能<graphic n="KR0263" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0263.png" mimeType="image/png"/>號　刋石叙<lb/>
