之風延熹六<graphic n="KR1013" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1013.png" mimeType="image/png"/>犬守東莱李君㦤其髙絜順天報國<lb/>
察舉孝㢘除郎中特慕供養常託疾在家時益部<lb/>
